Package: divR
Type: Package
Title: Distributional Instrumental Variable Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Anastasiia", "Holovchak", role = c("aut")),
    person("Sorawit", "Saengkyongam", role = "aut"),
    person("Nicolai", "Meinshausen", role = "aut"),
    person("Xinwei", "Shen", role = "aut"),
    person("Xian", "Gao", email = "xiangao@uchicago.edu", role = c("cre")))
Description: Implements Distributional Instrumental Variable (DIV) regression
    using energy score-based generative modelling via torch. Estimates the full
    interventional distribution P(Y|do(X)) in the presence of unmeasured
    confounding, yielding interventional means, quantiles, and samples.
    Based on Holovchak, Saengkyongam, Meinshausen & Shen (2025)
    <arXiv:2502.07641>.
